videos.headline: Miami with a trick play early in the game
videos.description: Runningback Phil Patterson gets the pitch and throws  it to quarterback Malik Rosier for a great reverse play for the Hurricanes.

videos.headline: Hurricanes' QB makes great 36 yard run
videos.description: Malik Rosier makes a great run for 36 yards to Virginia Tech's 2-yard line for first down.

videos.headline: Miami's Berrios with great jumping catch
videos.description: Hurricanes' Malik Rosier finds an open window and finds Braxton Berrios who makes a great jumping catch for a first down.

videos.headline: Miami picks up sack on third down
videos.description: Virginia Tech's Josh Jackson gets sacked by Miami's Amari Carter for a loss of 10 yards to force a punt,

videos.headline: Hurricanes on the board first with passing TD
videos.description: Miami's Malik Rosier finds Braxton Berrios for the first touchdown of the game in the second quarter.

videos.headline: Miami extends lead with a long TD run
videos.description: Hurricanes' Travis Homer receives the hand off and takes it to the house for a 64-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Hokies' QB Jackson with bad pitch
videos.description: Virginia Tech's Josh Jackson throws horrible pitch to Deshawn McClease who recovers the ball for a loss of 13 yards.

videos.headline: Virginia Tech with great interception
videos.description: Miami's Malik Rosier pass is intercepted by Hokies' Adonis Alexander and returns it for 18 yards.

videos.headline: Hokies' QB with a risky throw and a great catch
videos.description: Virginia Tech's Josh Jackson lobs the ball under pressure and finds Cam Phillips on the sidelines who times his jump perfectly to get the catch.

videos.headline: Hurricanes recover fumble to stop Hokies drive
videos.description: Virginia Tech's Sean Savory receives the pass and fumbles the ball, which is recovered by RJ McIntosh and he returns it for 35 yards.

videos.headline: Hokies' coach discusses late turnovers
videos.description: Virginia Tech's head coach Justin Fuente talks about the turnovers and the changes they need to make offensively.

videos.headline: Virginia Tech returns interception to the red zone
videos.description: Miami's Malik Rosier's pass is intercepted by Hokies' Reggie Floyd who tips it to himself and returns the ball for 37 yards.

videos.headline: Hokies cash in the interception with TD
videos.description: Josh Jackson gets pushed into the end zone by teammate Travon McMillian for a Virginia Tech touchdown.

videos.headline: Hurricanes' Rosier throws 3rd interception of the night
videos.description: Miami's quarterback Malik Rosier is picked off by Virginia Tech's Greg Stroman.

videos.headline: Miami bounces back with a passing TD
videos.description: Hurricanes' Malik Rosier connects with Christopher Herndon IV for a 43-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: MIAMI VS VT
Miami picks off Virginia Tech for the second time
videos.description: Hokies' Josh Jackson gets pressured and attempts to throw it to Cam Phillips but the ball sores over his head and the Hurricanes' Jaquan Johnson catches the ball and returns it for 20 yards.

videos.headline: Hurricanes' Rosier makes impressive throw for 1st down
videos.description: Malik Rosier finds Ahmmon Richards for 42 yards for a Miami first down.

videos.headline: Miami's QB runs in TD
videos.description: Hurricanes' Malik Rosier sees a split in the middle of the defense and runs up the middle for a 13-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Virginia Tech with their 3rd turnover of the game
videos.description: Hurricanes' Jonathan Garvin comes in from behind to sack Hokies' Josh Jackson, and recovers the ball.

videos.headline: Hurricanes picks off Hokies within last second of game
videos.description: Virginia Techs' Josh Jackson's pass is intercepted in the last seconds of the game by Miami's Sheldrick Redwin who returns it for 45 yards.

videos.headline: Miami QB Rosier discusses 28-10 victory over Virginia Tech
videos.description: Malik Rosier says the running game was electric and how Miami stays undefeated.

videos.headline: Miami remains undefeated with victory over VA Tech
videos.description: Malik Rosier and the Hurricanes keep an 8-0 record with a 28-10 victory over the Hokies.

videos.headline: Miami great performance leads them to victory over Virginia Tech
videos.description: ESPN analysis Kirk Herbstreit and Chris Fowler talk about how this was Miami's best performance this season, and their upcoming battle against Notre Dame.

videos.headline: Mark Richt discusses Miami's win despite mistakes
videos.description: Miami's head coach discusses how the Hurricanes played great despite turnovers, and what he told Malik Rosier after his three interceptions.

videos.headline: Hurricanes' Johnson talks about mentality of their defense
videos.description: Miami's DB Jaquan Johnson discusses how their defense battled through their interceptions, and how they wanted to match Virginia Techs' defense intensity.
